<section class="page-section grid" aria-label="Festival information">
  <div class="page-content">
    <div class="block center x-2 w-14 y-10 h-7">
      <div class="content-header">
        <h1>
          DOME DREAMING<br /><a
            href="https://calendar.google.com/calendar/render?action=TEMPLATE&text=Dome+Dreaming+Festival+%E2%80%93+Stockholm&dates=20260507T000000/20260510T000000&location=Stockholm"
            target="_blank"
            rel="noopener">
            Stockholm, 7–9 May</a
          >
          ·
          <a
            href="https://calendar.google.com/calendar/render?action=TEMPLATE&text=Dome+Dreaming+Festival+%E2%80%93+Malm%C3%B6&dates=20260512T000000/20260513T000000&location=Malm%C3%B6"
            target="_blank"
            rel="noopener">
            Malmö, 12 May</a
          >
        </h1>
      </div>
      <div class="content-main">
        <p>
          Fulldome film festival divided between Wisdome Stockholm and Malmö, two newly built state-of-the-art domes. Join the
          <a
            href="https://forms.gle/vatrcmZZBhLMNHsN7"
            target="_blank"
            rel="noopener"
            class="join-open-call"
            >open call</a
          >. Enter
          <button
            type="button"
            id="enter-dome-link"
            class="enter-dome-link"
            >the dome</button
          >
          and use our
          <a
            href="https://preview.domedreaming.com/"
            target="_blank"
            rel="noopener"
            >preview tool</a
          >. Full programme released in March.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="content-logos logos">
        {% for logo in logos.partners %}
        <a href="{{ logo.href }}" target="_blank" rel="noopener">
          <img src="{{ logo.src }}" alt="{{ logo.alt }}" width="80" height="40" loading="lazy" decoding="async" />
        </a>
        {% endfor %}
      </div>

      <div class="content-credits">
        <p class="small">
          Dome Dreaming is a non-profit festival produced by
          <a
            href="https://www.jonasjohansson.se/"
            target="_blank"
            rel="noopener"
            >Jonas Johansson</a
          >,
          <a
            href="https://www.ivar.studio/"
            target="_blank"
            rel="noopener"
            >Fredrik Edström</a
          >
          and
          <a
            href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/sebastian-h%C3%A4ger-53054b155/"
            target="_blank"
            rel="noopener"
            >Sebastian Häger</a
          >, in collaboration with
          <a
            href="https://aavistusfestival.fi"
            target="_blank"
            rel="noopener"
            >Aavistus</a
          >,
          <a
            href="https://www.instagram.com/kokongfestival/"
            target="_blank"
            rel="noopener"
            >Kokong</a
          >,
          <a
            href="https://www.balticanaloglab.lv/"
            target="_blank"
            rel="noopener"
            >Baltic Analog Lab</a
          >
          and
          <a
            href="https://www.nava.community"
            target="_blank"
            rel="noopener"
            >Nordic Audiovisual Artists</a
          >. Student day in coordination with
          <a
            href="https://kkh.se/"
            target="_blank"
            rel="noopener"
            >KKH</a
          >,
          <a
            href="https://www.uniarts.se/"
            target="_blank"
            rel="noopener"
            >SKH</a
          >,
          <a
            href="https://konstfack.se/"
            target="_blank"
            rel="noopener"
            >Konstfack</a
          >
          and
          <a
            href="https://www.ostragreviefolkhogskola.com/"
            target="_blank"
            rel="noopener"
            >Östra Grevie Folkhögskola</a
          >. Supported by
          <a
            href="https://www.tekniskamuseet.se/"
            target="_blank"
            rel="noopener"
            >Tekniska museet</a
          >,
          <a
            href="https://malmo.se/"
            target="_blank"
            rel="noopener"
            >Malmö Stad</a
          >
          and
          <a
            href="https://www.regionstockholm.se/"
            target="_blank"
            rel="noopener"
            >Region Stockholm</a
          >. 3D model by
          <a
            href="https://smash.studio/"
            target="_blank"
            rel="noopener"
            >Ashley Reed</a
          >. Original dome visualiser by <a href="https://www.instagram.com/possan/" rel="noopener">Per-Olov Jernberg</a>. Design and development by
          <a
            href="https://jonasjohansson.se/"
            target="_blank"
            rel="noopener"
            >Jonas Johansson</a
          >.
        </p>
        <p class="xsmall">Dome Dreaming is not affiliated with Wisdome or Norrköping Visualiseringscenter.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div id="canvas-container" aria-hidden="true">
    <div id="drop-zone"></div>
  </div>
</section>
